Abuja- The Peoples Democratic Party on Tuesday raised alarm over plot by some elements to disorganize the party in Osun state. To this end, the party alerted Nigerians of clandestine plots by certain individuals to set up a strange office in Osogbo, Osun state, and purport such to be the Osun State secretariat of the PDP. For the avoidance of doubts, the PDP stated in unequivocal terms that “our legitimate state secretariat in Osun State remains our office located at Km 3, Ikirun Road, beside Federal Road Safety Corps Office, Biket Area, Osogbo, Osun state.” ABUJA DOCTOR REVEALS HOW MOST NIGERIA MEN ARE NOW OVERCOMING TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS BRILLIANT DISCOVERY. DON'T BE A VICTIM! PDP, in a statement by its spokesman, Kola Ologbondiyan said that “it is imperative to state that our great party does not operate or recognize any other state secretariat in Osun State other than the above stated.” “All party members, critical stakeholders and supporters, particularly in Osun state and the nation at large, the Independent National Electoral Commission (INEC), all security agencies, the media and the general public should take note and be guided by this accordingly.” APC ‘ll Not To Be Distracted By PDP’s Ranting-Caretaker Committee Ekpa Vows To Showcase Her Passion In Gender, Women Welfare “The leadership of the PDP charges all our members in Osun state to continue to work together and not be distracted by any such divisive plots, especially at this time that our party is working relentlessly to rescue our nation from misrule.”